Early years ==
Maisonave was born on June 30, 1930  in Old San Juan, Puerto Rico, where he attended Abraham Lincoln High School.
In 1947, his family moved to New York City, where he graduated from William John Gaynor High School in 1948 (P. S 49 in Brooklyn).
